reviewText: Great price, great for the family
Very cute DVD. The kids loved it but one (age 5yrs) found the Teeny Tiny story a little scary.

I had searched years for this story. I had the title wrong but Amazon had enough detailed info in their description that it picked up right away the story I was searching for. You delighted my daughter and grandchildren.
Great read along for kids.the read alone options on the video help kids see and hear the words in the story. My loftily girl loves these spooky story's! Great for fall time and good famaly watch.
